    <div class="content">
        <div class="ttypography"><p>Hello Codeforces!</p><p>We are really excited to invite you to participate in <a href="/contest/2210" title="Codeforces Round 1089 (Div. 2)">Codeforces Round 1089 (Div. 2)</a>, which will be held on <a class="contest-time" contestid="2210" href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?day=29&amp;month=3&amp;year=2026&amp;hour=17&amp;min=35&amp;sec=0&amp;p1=166"><span class="format-time-with-dow">Mar/29/2026 17:35 (Moscow time)</span></a>. </p><p>You will be given <strong>$$$6$$$ &quot;simple&quot; problems</strong> and <strong>$$$2$$$ hour $$$15$$$ minutes</strong> to solve them. Note that one of the problems will be further divided into $$$2$$$ subtasks. Furthermore, some of the problems may be interactive, so please <a href="https://codeforces.com/blog/entry/45307">read the guide for interactive problems</a> if you are not familiar with them. This round will be <strong>rated</strong> for the participants with rating <strong>lower</strong> than 2100.</p><p>The scoring distribution is as follows: <table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;text-align: center;margin: auto;">  <thead>  <tr style="background-color: rgb(240,240,240);">  <th style="text-align: center;">A</th>  <th style="text-align: center;">B</th>  <th style="text-align: center;">C</th>  <th style="text-align: center;">D</th>  <th style="text-align: center;">E</th>  <th style="text-align: center;">F</th>  </tr>  </thead>  <tbody>  <tr>  <td>$$$500$$$</td>  <td>$$$1000$$$</td>  <td>$$$(1250+1000)$$$</td>  <td>$$$2250$$$</td>  <td>$$$2750$$$</td>  <td>$$$3500$$$</td>  </tr>  </tbody> </table></p><p>The problems are authored and prepared by <a class="rated-user user-blue" href="/profile/simplelife" title="Expert simplelife">simplelife</a>, <a class="rated-user user-blue" href="/profile/ritam1234" title="Expert ritam1234">ritam1234</a>, <a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/__baozii__" title="International Grandmaster __baozii__">__baozii__</a>, and me. </p><p>We would really like to thank the following people for making this round possible:</p> <ul>   <li><a class="rated-user user-orange" href="/profile/cry" title="International Master cry">cry</a> for his orz coordination and support throughout the round, <s>and also for rejecting a lot of problems.</s></li>   <li><a class="rated-user user-orange" href="/profile/Alexdat2000" title="Master Alexdat2000">Alexdat2000</a> for Russian translation.</li>   <li><a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/__baozii__" title="International Grandmaster __baozii__">__baozii__</a>, <a class="rated-user user-blue" href="/profile/wuhudsm" title="Expert wuhudsm">wuhudsm</a> and <a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/Intellegent" title="Grandmaster Intellegent">Intellegent</a> for VVIP testing.</li>   <li><a class="rated-user user-orange" href="/profile/VladiG" title="Master VladiG">VladiG</a>, <a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/sammyuri" title="International Grandmaster sammyuri">sammyuri</a> and <a class="rated-user user-violet" href="/profile/macaquedev" title="Candidate Master macaquedev">macaquedev</a> for their &quot;Special Contribution&quot;.</li>   <li><a class="rated-user user-legendary" href="/profile/Dominater069" title="Legendary Grandmaster Dominater069"><span class="legendary-user-first-letter">D</span>ominater069</a> for LGM testing</li>   <li><a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/kevinxiehk" title="Grandmaster kevinxiehk">kevinxiehk</a>, <a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/awesomeguy856" title="Grandmaster awesomeguy856">awesomeguy856</a>, <a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/sammyuri" title="International Grandmaster sammyuri">sammyuri</a>, <a class="rated-user user-red" href="/profile/_istil" title="Grandmaster _istil">_istil</a> for Red testing.</li>   <li><a class="rated-user user-orange" href="/profile/amsraman" title="Master amsraman">amsraman</a>, <a class="rated-user 